item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

[quote=“iz3 legend, post:1, topic:392554”]well first off how would i change the text in this tab? i tried client.java and playerassistant but couldnt find it.

Also how would i change the title of my client above file, i thought it was located in gui.java but this client doesnt have one =( if you could help me id love you[/quote]

Chances are it’s either programmed into the interface (client-side changes required), or it’s in a different class. Best advice I can give is search for one of those strings in all your server files. If it doesn’t appear there, then check for client-side changes.
